Self-reported sleep duration in the analytical sample was 7.2 hours (SD = 1.1), mean PSQI sleep-quality component scores were 1.3 (SD = 0.6), mean daytime sleepiness was 5.6 on the Epworth Sleepiness Scale (SD = 3.5), and mean wellbeing was 23.2 on the SWEMWBS (SD = 5.0).


